Text: Huff...huff...
Well done, Lady Gamma!
I-I really thought I was dead!

Yeah, but you aren't. In other words...the magic
gear experiment was a huge success.
I'm too tired to even be mad at youâ€”
Lady Gamma!

...Wish she'd hung in there a little longer. Still
haven't finished...all of today's experiments.
Is there something else you want to try?

Yeah...operational testing...of this defense
facility. Need to test...with slime. Wanted
to test together...with magic gear.
How about using me as a test subject?

You're too strong...Lady Alpha... Don't think I'd
get...good data...

If a strong individual were to increase their
strength with magic gear, wouldn't that data
be useful in its own right?
Well, I guess.
...Yeah, might be fun...checking those results.

Then it's settled. Lambda! Prepare the best magic
gear you currently have available!
Sir! Yes sir!
...Alright...advance forward...
Understood. Can I take them all out?
Take out...anything that turns up...if you can.
Th-This is turning into...quite the serious battle!
Lambda, begin.
Sir! Yes sir!

My body feels lighter than usual! The magic gear must
be working.
Lady Alpha...what strength!

I can understand why Lady Eta was reluctant to use
Lady Alpha. The data's not very useful since it's
hard to measure the magic gear's enhancing effect!
Heheh...!

Did she just laugh?! Don't tell me she has something
else up her sleeve!

Now then, all that's left is the area at the far end.
Are we done with the golems and the slime?
...Your opponent...is neither slime...nor golem...
Oh? Then what am I up against?
Awoooo!!!
Lady Delta?!
Oooh! It's Alpha!

Hey, Eta! You said this was an experiment where I
could take out anyone who showed up here, right?
...Yeah. I did.

So...you can take out Lady Alpha. That's the sort of
experiment...I'm conducting.
Lady Eta! Isn't this taking things too farâ€”
If I take out Lady Alpha here...
No way! That'll make me the number two of the pack!
What did you say?
Oh!
Agh...!
...Eta.
Hm?

You said I can take out "anything that turns up,"
correct?
Sure. Be my guest.
Well then, with pleasureâ€”
I-I won't chicken out today! I'm gonna win!
